  "title": "Sales and Marketing Manager (Oil & Gas Industry) - S$5,000 basic + AWS",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Sales & Marketing Manager</strong></h2><h3><strong>Additional Information</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Up to $5,000 basic + S$800 Transport Allowance + Bonus + AWS</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Location: </strong>Ubi Crescent</p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong>5-day work week, 8:30am – 6:00pm</p></li><li><p><strong>Annual Leave: </strong>14 days</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Lead sales and business development activities for the assigned market/territory.</p></li><li><p>Develop and implement effective sales and marketing plans to achieve targeted sales results.</p></li><li><p>Participate in technical clarifications and discussions based on customers’ requirements.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with customers and design engineers to specify suitable products and solutions.</p></li><li><p>Actively explore new business opportunities and expand market share across key industries.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Electrical / Electronics Engineering.</p></li><li><p>Minimum <strong>5 years of sales experience</strong> with strong industry contacts, preferably in:</p><ul><li><p>Marine</p></li><li><p>Oil & Gas / Petrochemical</p></li><li><p>Utilities & Power Plants</p></li><li><p>EPC Contractors</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal, communication, and relationship-building skills.</p></li><li><p>Good presentation and negotiation skills.</p></li><li><p>Must possess a <strong>valid Class 3 driving licence and own a car</strong>. Frequently travelling to client site to be expected.</p></li><li><p>Candidates from the <strong>Oil & Gas sector</strong> will be preferred.</p></li></ul>",
